{"tid":2240901,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳家樂舊愛驚爆未婚懷孕 27歲余香凝傳下月趕奉子成婚 Jennifer未有否認","createTime":"2020-10-13T03:41:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-13T06:06:55.000Z","uid":147522,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d64c719c3dad4655ec150cb5b12fdc7bf01fe6d3","tid":2240901,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T03:41:16.000Z","msg":"27歲女藝人余香凝，被爆出未婚懷孕的消息，有報道更指Jennifer打算下個月趕住奉子成婚。余香凝曾與藝人陳家樂有過一段情，兩人曾交往三年多，後來分手，有傳女方搭上保險才俊Victor。<br />\n<br />\n余香凝最近接受訪問自爆渴望成家立室，不過就表示仍未有男友。有報道指她未婚懷孕兼下月奉子成婚，而經手人是圈外人。余香凝對此未有否認，只是表示不回應私人事。而她最近在IG曬靚相並表示「紀錄這一刻」，已有網民猜測其懷孕，更有人留言「人逢喜事精神爽」。<br />\n<br />\n陳家樂被問及舊愛婚訊，就表示不便回應余小姐的私人事。今年陳家樂被指與連詩雅撻著，兩人為了保護愛苗，行事相當低調。"},{"pid":"f6cea6ecee951a4c87efa28f49a453514d629c12","tid":2240901,"uid":180401,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T03:41:43.000Z","msg":"who?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c43e0fa38cfa8a344a78da813d6558a488cef4dd","tid":2240901,"uid":40615,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T03:43:13.000Z","msg":"who ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e132ec361484a215ec6548a7f17a79b299a855","tid":2240901,"uid":209241,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T03:46:06.000Z","msg":"做戲成日做呀媽搞到真係變呀媽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ce63c11886a6935144a52f7ad05b3ebbe58c1e","tid":2240901,"uid":76804,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T03:46:52.000Z","msg":"一隻臭雞<br />\n一件英皇愛國撚樣<br />\n是撚旦啦"},{"pid":"c0f44afa827ea30dfdd9be61bf06a7099c76b339","tid":2240901,"uid":57776,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T03:47:13.000Z","msg":"雞。。。"},{"pid":"928e538e8053e8998366c71f050289b6555faa63","tid":2240901,"uid":55960,"like":0,"dislike"